io.netty.handler.codec

Interface ConvertibleHeaders<UnconvertedType,ConvertedType>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Headers<UnconvertedType>, Iterable<Map.Entry<UnconvertedType,UnconvertedType>>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SpdyHeaders, StompHeaders, TextHeaders
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultConvertibleHeaders, DefaultSpdyHeaders, DefaultStompHeaders, DefaultTextHeaders, EmptyConvertibleHeaders, EmptyTextHeaders

    public interface ConvertibleHeaders<UnconvertedType,ConvertedType>
extends Headers<UnconvertedType>
    Extension to the Headers interface to provide methods which convert the native UnconvertedType to the not-native ConvertedType
